dct_title_s: Melbourne and suburbs / compiled at the Dept. of Lands and Survey, Melbourne by F.S. Hilcke
dct_description_sm: Detailed street map showing municipal and parish boundaries, railways and stations, electric tramways, schools, and post offices. "March 1923 revised Nov. 1956." "Drawn and reproduced at the Dept. of Lands and Survey Melbourne, Victoria." Ancillary map of Port Phillip Bay showing ports distance to Melbourne. Index to sheets of the Dandenong ranges area; 10 chains series. Districts are color coded Map shows roads, streets, municipal and parish boundaries, railways, stations, electric tramways, post offices and state schools.
dct_creator_sm: Victoria. Department of Crown Lands and Survey
dct_publisher_sm: Melbourne : Dept. of Lands and Survey Melbourne, 1956.
